1. jshERP (管伊佳ERP)
   Copyright (c) Ji Shenghua and contributors
   Source: https://github.com/jishenghua/jshERP
   License: Apache License 2.0
   Used for: Core PSI domain entities (depot_head/depot_item universal
             document model, material/SKU schema, account/finance
             ledger structure, weighted-average-cost algorithm
             reference). Translated to PostgreSQL DDL with
             multi-tenant RLS isolation, snake_case naming,
             tenant_id row-level security, soft-delete via
             deleted_at TIMESTAMPTZ, PostgreSQL native arrays
             replacing CSV string fields.

