   Used for: Warehouse management module schema (six-state stock
             fields: on_hand/available/reserved/in_transit/damage/hold;
             ASN/receiving/picking/putaway workflow patterns;
             location/bin hierarchy). Adapted from Django models to
             Go GORM entities.

3. Apache OFBiz
   Copyright (c) The Apache Software Foundation
   Source: https://github.com/apache/ofbiz-framework
   License: Apache License 2.0
   Used for: Order/Inventory/Facility entity design patterns;
             InventoryItem variance handling; serial number tracking;
             general ledger account code structure (referenced for
             v2 finance integration design).

